➜生活需要足球的激情，也需要享受“瓦罐”的人生
http://www.sohu.com/a/430895544_179848	12694
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201110/e33daa615e444535bd7b82c77836078d.gif" /></p>
<p><strong>两队对攻</strong><strong>7</strong><strong>球，“进”无止境</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>11</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>月</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>7</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>日，一场别开生面的</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>长安福特上海媒体足球友谊赛</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>于上海泽竞北岸球场正式拉开战幕。随着裁判一声哨响，在这场三节共</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>90</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>分钟的</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>7</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>人制比赛中，由上海汽车媒体人组成的</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>雄起不得虚队</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>与</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>硬质模子队</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>展开了一番激烈的较量。</span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img width="328" src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201110/3575bebd9f3145dfaad249cc32527a8b.jpeg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">球场上，来自长安福特的赵非先生和陈晓波先生与上海媒体同仁共同享受足球带来的快乐。经过双方激烈的争夺，两支球队联手奉献了一场精彩的比赛。</span></p>
<p><img width="328" src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201110/a84a01f726544e8793c4fd64c70f2b11.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
