<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p><img width="328" src="//p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201110/34c5c41236e74ec3af53cf8b34315dcb.jpeg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>最终，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>雄起不得虚队</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>以</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>4</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>3</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>的比分险胜</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>硬质模子队</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>，取得了本场赛事的胜利。全场比赛，双方共射入</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>7</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>颗进球，正所谓：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>进</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>无止境！在场上时每一位</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>球员</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>都拼劲了全力，挥汗如雨，享受比赛。</span></span></span></span></p>
<p><strong>福克斯“瓦罐”惊艳亮相</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>本次活动长安福特还带来了一个大大的惊喜。伴随裁判的一声长哨，中场比赛结束休息时，长安福特的赵总和陈总呼着诸位媒体老师一起去场边拿饮用水和毛巾休息。结果来到车前却让我们大家眼前一亮，出现在我们眼前的居然是一辆福克斯</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>瓦罐</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>！虽然福克斯</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>瓦罐</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>已经遍布欧洲的大街小巷，但能在国内见到这台车确实颇感意外。这瞬间就勾引起了各位媒体老师的求知欲。</span></span></span></span></p>
<p><img width="328" src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201110/713c893991e54e008479e42d77086feb.jpeg" /></p>
<p><img width="328" src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201110/8ea61758689948af8c6dea8c2230812e.jpeg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>当赵总打开福克斯</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>瓦罐</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>后备厢的那一刻，看到后备厢里装满的各种用品，不得不说让我们有点</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>惊住了</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>。有那么一瞬间，心中生出了</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>羡慕</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>之情。想想平时自己要是也能有这么一辆福克斯</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>瓦罐</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>，周末开着去踢球；又或者带着家人去郊游，后备厢装满家人需要的敞篷、行李箱、野餐炊具等。</span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img width="328" src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201110/9a5e72985fd7498e9d2d39472f9d625f.jpeg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>光是想想，就很羡慕这样的生活方式，或许真的只有在那一刻因为才在球场上挥汗，场下休息时，能够看到充足的</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>后备厢补给</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>，就会让人觉得更加心安，也更理解这种</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>瓦罐</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>的生活方式。</span></span></span></span></p>
<p><strong>瓦罐文化或将迎来春天</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>瓦罐</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>在欧洲代表了品质生活，是欧洲人心目中</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>实用性</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>和</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>驾驶 乐趣 </span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>结合的完美车型。</span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img width="328" src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201110/f9a004fac58445dea8a5d5781d7c6b24.jpeg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>以往的数据不看，就</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>2020</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>年欧洲上半年</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>C-SW</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>级别瓦罐车，总体销量达到了惊人的</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>255,300</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>辆，这其中排行第一的正是福克斯</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>瓦罐</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>。此前，标致、大众、通用等合资品牌以及奔驰、宝马等豪华品牌都将旗下的旅行轿车引入国内市场，比普通三厢车型贵出许多，使其俨然成为一种品质、尊荣的象征。</span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img width="328" src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201110/8a27aa4035684576a592df4d322a260a.jpeg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">但随着中国汽车市场的高速发展，尤其是在疫情之后，国内消费群体购车的理念也越来越成熟，特别是年轻购车群体的快速崛起，国人已经逐渐接受瓦罐车的概念，瓦罐车的多功能以及实用性很好地契合了中国家庭。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img width="328" src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201110/1e12e4bfc7ad4f29b82bb2752d16f96d.jpeg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span>尤其是如今的年轻消费者在选择家用车型时，更多会从实际需求出发。当有自己想法的年轻消费者越来越多的同时，瓦罐文化或许将在国内迎来春天。而福克斯</span></span><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span><span><span>瓦罐</span></span><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span><span><span>毫无疑问会成为长安福特未来在中国市场极为重要的战略车型。</span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>而最后值得一提的是，在足球赛当天，长安福特的领导给大家透露出了个重磅消息</span></span><span><span><span><span>——</span></span></span></span><span><span>长安福特福克斯</span></span><span><span><span><span>“</span></span></span></span><span><span>瓦罐</span></span><span><span><span><span>”</span></span></span></span><span><span>将在</span></span><span><span><span><span>11</span></span></span></span><span><span>月</span></span><span><span><span><span>20</span></span></span></span><span><span>日广州车展正式上市。毫无疑问，它必将成为广州车展上的重磅车型之一。我们也期待它的到来，能助力中国的瓦罐车文化得到健康发展。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>